# BUT track the ear-validated emotion-band (L16-26) packs in git — the regression of
# 2026-06-15 was caused by a validated .expr being gitignored, overwritten and lost with
# no backup (see regression_lora.md). Tracking the *_l1626_* packs prevents a recurrence.
# (Broad-band *_bb027_* and paralinguistic_* experiments stay ignored — heavy + unvalidated.)
!presets/expr/*_l1626_*.expr
